author: Maria Armental
title: Take-Two, SVB Financial and Nektar Therapeutics to Join S&P 500
text:
Take-Two Interactive Software Inc., SVB Financial Group and Nektar Therapeutics are joining the S&P 500 index, according to S&P Dow Jones Indices.
The companies will replace Signet Jewelers Ltd., Patterson Cos. and Chesapeake Energy Corp., which will be moving to the S&P MidCap 400.
